{"tid":8092,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人民幣持續貶值人民日報呼籲勿盲目跟風兌換外幣","createTime":"2016-11-28T06:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T00:58:34.000Z","uid":30169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d14b46933a6177d15252fef47c03d4e0c47dfef","tid":8092,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/finance/人民幣持續貶值-人民日報-呼籲-勿盲目跟風兌換外幣/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2-%E5%8B%BF%E7%9B%B2%E7%9B%AE%E8%B7%9F%E9%A2%A8%E5%85%8C%E6%8F%9B%E5%A4%96%E5%B9%A3%2F&d=GWE3d9Tn9k6wFOfB12cPS8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=557f64cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2-%E5%8B%BF%E7%9B%B2%E7%9B%AE%E8%B7%9F%E9%A2%A8%E5%85%8C%E6%8F%9B%E5%A4%96%E5%B9%A3%2F&h=f07d8cc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/finance/人民幣持續貶值-人民日報-呼籲-勿盲目跟風兌換外幣/</a><br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》今天刊出長篇報道，通過採訪專家和居民，稱人民幣匯率基本穩定，不存在長期貶值基礎，呼籲不要盲目跟風兌換外匯。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，近來人民幣匯率下行主要是因為美元太強，同期人民幣對一籃子貨幣基本穩定，也不存在長期貶值基礎。<br />\n<br />\n文章引述中金所研究院首席經濟學家趙慶明分析，近期美國聯儲局加息預期增強，推動美元指數上升，包括人民幣在內的非美元貨幣都對美元出現了貶值。若進行橫向比較，人民幣跌幅在全球範圍內並不算大。11月以來，受美元指數上漲影響，全球主要發達國家和新興市場貨幣普遍下跌，100多種貨幣對美元有不同程度的貶值。受到美國大選影響，短期內美元指數最大漲幅超過6%。相比美元對日元漲幅10%左右、對歐元在8%至10%左右，人民幣對美元跌幅也只有4.5%左右。<br />\n<br />\n文章稱，個人換外匯要根據自身需求，不宜盲目跟風兌換。如果短期內無剛需，沒有必要提前換匯。又指相比人民幣，美元存款利率及理財產品收益率並無太大優勢。高風險、高回報的外幣產品也不適合穩健型投資者。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述趙慶明認為，人民幣理財收益率總體依然高過外匯理財收益率，市面上的外幣理財產品相對不多，無論是流動性還是收益率，都無法與人民幣理財產品比肩。並且，人民幣匯率並不具備大幅貶值空間，人民幣投資組合收益率超過貶值幅度的可能性很大，普通投資者還是以投資人民幣理財產品為宜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5045daba35787ccaf916d7ab001ff41dc5193be","tid":8092,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"同佢相反就搵大錢"},{"pid":"ba0403c248a8b0b7e4734de0d54340a538319976","tid":8092,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢相反就搵大錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06752a1ac08b40ea3a028d52ca4fd0ef0d4f6d32","tid":8092,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce866e38b97ec82efc6f4d5541e7df6418804d14","tid":8092,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c14ce0cebdeb6878d93c875aa02a6168432d601","tid":8092,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"人無貶基"},{"pid":"c37a3017e82abc36c538da5ea4abb491737c4b1f","tid":8092,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人無貶基</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下聨係乜"},{"pid":"2a5c13e29b224adb6e4ccb550aa47955a2e86158","tid":8092,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"係咪可以瘋狂沽人仔喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cce5913b173174cf36a18c04eab107b4124d85","tid":8092,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人無貶基</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n領導走先"},{"pid":"a37df365be6846a6a77abc96603ac9ae21558995","tid":8092,"uid":31269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T0